column2: select top #  s.objid, p.petroRad_r from specphoto s  join  galSpecExtra g  on  g.specobjid = s.specobjid  join  photoobjall p  on  p.objid = s.objid  join  zooSpec z  on  z.objid = s.objid where  p.clean = #  and  (p.calibStatus_r & p.calibStatus_g & p.calibStatus_i & p.calibStatus_u & p.calibStatus_z & #) != #  and  (p.flags_r & dbo.fPhotoFlags(&&&)) > #
